all or might send the messages directly to you.  You have been very
consistent in merely restating your positions, not responding to
reasoned arguments.  This motivates the sort of messages you have been
receiving, since unanswered statements on mailing lists are sometimes
interpreted as vaild or correct becausae they go unchallenged.

